{
  "chapter": 60,
  "chapter_summary": "第六十回　情根深种。剑客行故事继续。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "神龙太子",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "神龙太子",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莫非她怀孕了……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "神龙太子",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "很多是非一言两语说不清楚，我只告诉太子一件事，教主乘舟过海，遇到飓风，船毁人亡，教主以下，全船二百余人无一幸免……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "神龙太子",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你以为贫道会说假话吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "神龙太子",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "太仓之鼠",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还有，",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
