      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "银扇子",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "银扇子",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "随又转头对女儿道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "痴儿……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有这等事？你妹妹现在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她已战死。就躺在那里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她还有救吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不要扶她站起，要她静坐调治一会就好了……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此乃千年'灵芝仙液'，功可白骨生肉，起死回生！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哇！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说起来她们也不是外人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "随又一指樊素鸾道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "银扇子",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "转又对雷大叔道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "武林四公子",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "武林四公子",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "随又转问雷大叔道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "武林四公子",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "端方公子",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "如果不是有洞庭湖之变，你们都是通家之好，不但是朋友，还是亲戚呢……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "侄女与展小侠就是要做这样的朋友！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "朋友",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "红粉酬知己",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "把展贤侄埋葬以后呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "四女守坟？世界再大，恐怕也不会有这等新鲜事吧……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "江南七侠",
      "tone": "陈述",
