      "text": "灵芝仙液",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "柳贤弟，真神人也。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "展哥哥，你身上还会痛吧？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "白哥，你感觉内腑怎么样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "展哥……小侠，你的伤好了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我已经好了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他的伤势尚未复原，不宜起来行动，还是多调息一会儿……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "贤侄免礼！贤侄免礼！",
